'backup' can now be used with a description included
eg. backup 3 d/April 2023

New commands:
viewbackup: shows all the backups available
deletebackup INDEX: deletes a backup from a specified index
eg. deletebackup 3

As there are now 2 different interfaces, one listing the persons and one listing the backups, all other commands now automatically redirect one to the persons page.
